@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lyfums(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.64)) - wp.sin((v1 + 0.96 - tmp + 0.68)))
    tmp = wp.cos(v1)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.96 / v0 + 0.38)))
    data[tid] = v0
